reviewText: Powerful.  The images are still on our minds.  This movie pulls no punches, yet its very endearing.  AN original voice in filmmaking.

I purchased this product in error believing that it was Monday Mornings TV show and after partially watching it I ended up throwing this movie in the trash as I didn't want it as a part of my movie collection.  The harsh realities of life we are faced with practically everyday and I don't need a movie to remind me of them.
